title: Congressman-Elect Ronny Jackson: Pennsylvania “Engineered” Counting Their Votes
summary:
Email Embed+ Embed CodeEmbed the following code on your website:Watch the latest video at foxnews.comOn Fox Across America with Jimmy Failla, Congressman-Elect and former White House Physician Dr. Ronny Jackson talks to Jimmy about his win in Texas & the chaos happening in Pennsylvania with the counting of the votes.
"I know we got to figure this out.
The fact that even before the election happened, Pennsylvania was basically telling everybody they're not going to really have an answer for quite some time, we're going to do this and we're going to do that.
And and they really laid the groundwork for what's happening right now.
It tells you that they engineered it this way, they brought this upon themselves and they did it for a specific purpose because they did it because they want to be able to determine what the outcome is, if need be."
